(1038, 1, '2015-10-30 14:07:05', '2015-10-30 13:07:05', '<h1 class="p1" style="text-align: center;">Sally Wiola Sessions</h1>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;">Never Stop Dreaming. Sally Wiola Session is new coming projec,t where sofia release other Musicians, on her own label.<span class="Apple-converted-space">  </span>In the year of 2016 there will be 3 releases in a Suit, called Sally Wiola Sessons 1 , 2 and 3. The suit will contain/behold instrumental music only, of course by topnotch-musicians of sweden in different genres. Sally Wiola Sessions will be produced by Sofia and released worldwide.</p>\r\n<p class="p1" style="text-align: center;">Sofia invited Peter Holgersson so Check out the first recordingsession in October this year at\r\n<a href="http://www.peterholgersson.se/2015/10/17/lisa-och-lisa-i-studion/" target="_blank">http://www.peterholgersson.se/2015/10/17/lisa-och-lisa-i-studion/</a>.\r\nLisa Rydberg (fiddle) and Lisa Långbacka (accordion ) will be the first release 2016.</p>', 'Sally Wiola Sessions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '799-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-30 14:07:05', '2015-10-30 13:07:05', '', 799, 'http://www.sofiakarlsson.com/799-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
